HEADWORD: Stibiated
<hw>Stib"i*a`ted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[NL.
<ets>stibiatus</ets>, from L. <ets>stibium</ets> antimony.]</ety>
